jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Offset-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Offset-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/offset">Offset</a>宣布了他的第二张专辑《Set It Off》，并分享了他最新单曲《Fan》的视频。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/migos-cover-interview-2021-culture-iii-2976980">封面上的 Migos：“我们带着货物出现并证明你错了”</a></strong></li></ul><p>由说唱歌手亲自执导的《Fan》视频中 Offset 向传奇人物迈克尔·杰克逊致敬。美国女演员 Paige Hurd、YouTube 用户和 Twitch 主播 Kai Cenat 和 Fanum 均出席了该节目。这首歌由 Aaron Bow、FNZ、Teddy Walton、Thank You Fizzle 和 Thurdi 制作。</p><p> Offset 在一份声明中谈到这首歌和即将发行的专辑时表示：“我已经为这个项目工作了两年多。这个赛季对我来说是个人的。它标志着我人生的新篇章。</p><p> “我感觉就像迈克尔·杰克逊一样，从一个打破纪录的成功团体，独自成为超级巨星。这些作品对我来说是一种治愈，也是一封写给我的粉丝和支持者的信。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Offset - FAN（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mt6wxhwMBs4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/migos">Migos</a>说唱歌手一段时间以来一直在预告<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/offset-father-of-4-review-2453677">他 2019 年首张专辑《Father Of 4》的</a>后续作品。</p><p>去年 11 月，他本来应该放弃这张专辑，然而，出于对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/takeoff-killed-aged-28-migos-houston-3340227">已故朋友和乐队成员 Takeoff 去世的</a>尊重， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/offset-delays-release-of-new-album-following-takeoffs-death-3347671">他推迟了这张专辑</a>，从那以后粉丝们一直想知道这张专辑什么时候会发行。 Offset 在与 Ebro Darden 的<em>Apple Music 1</em>聊天时告诉电台名人，这张专辑“将于 10 月推出，但现在我们只是施加压力”。</p><p> 《Set It Off》将于 10 月 13 日通过 Motown Records 发行。<a href="https://offset.lnk.to/SetItOff" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预先保存/预订专辑。</p><p>该密纹唱片还收录了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardi-b">Cardi B</a>协助的 7 月 28 日发行的《Jealousy》。《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/three-6-mafia">Three 6 Mafia》</a>采样曲目是他们作为情侣的最新合作，标志着这对夫妻第六次合作。合作了一首曲目。其他包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/migos-nicki-minaj-cardi-b-release-new-track-motorsport-2154082">“MotorSport”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/offset-cardi-b-perform-clout-jimmy-kimmel-live-hollywood-streets-2530507">“Clout”</a> 。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxLjI2NRfV_/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.88